        "TileImage": "$($repository e1c8c0a5-a506-45b6-9567-7b6df50b8877).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to Dubai 47\r\rYour ultimate test of patience and endurance begins! Sheikh Omar was always in our Hit list and now we have a perfect opportunity to get him out of the way. Make sure you make it look like an accident and also get rid off his two guards and lastly his secretary who is disguised as a Tech Crew, all must be accidents! Burj al Ghazali opening is the prefect cover you have got.\r\rGood Hunting",
